  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a universe full of secrets, you take on the role of a brave astronaut in search of space relics. Explore this vast universe, traverse territories, and dodge asteroids while uncovering rare artifacts lost in the cosmos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/2227b0ad1a80a19d2c82ff6520f61f78.poster.avif?t=1754410258\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/2227b0ad1a80a19d2c82ff6520f61f78.webm?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/2227b0ad1a80a19d2c82ff6520f61f78.mp4?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME MODES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the mysteries of the universe in Story Mode or test your reflexes in Infinite Run. Take on three challenging minigames: <i>All Sides</i> tests your reaction time, <i>Planet Hop</i> requires precision, and <i>Zero-Gravity Pool</i> brings strategic challenges in weightlessness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/11b142342bf4ec5812acfc8c9385aff0.poster.avif?t=1754410258\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/11b142342bf4ec5812acfc8c9385aff0.webm?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/11b142342bf4ec5812acfc8c9385aff0.mp4?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> – Embark on an immersive journey through the universe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relic Collection</strong> – Discover and catalog unique space artifacts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill Tree</strong> – Enhance your journey with strategic upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of Skins</strong> – Unlock unique outfits for your character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space Challenges</strong> – Overcome obstacles and prove your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Territory Exploration</strong> – Conquer and discover new regions of space.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progress and Achievements</strong> – Complete objectives and unlock trophies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller Support</strong> – Compatible with Xbox 360, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, and PlayStation 4/5 (Bluetooth and USB).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Space holds many secrets... are you ready to uncover them?</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a universe full of secrets, you take on the role of a brave astronaut in search of space relics. Explore this vast universe, traverse territories, and dodge asteroids while uncovering rare artifacts lost in the cosmos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/2227b0ad1a80a19d2c82ff6520f61f78.poster.avif?t=1754410258\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/2227b0ad1a80a19d2c82ff6520f61f78.webm?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/2227b0ad1a80a19d2c82ff6520f61f78.mp4?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME MODES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the mysteries of the universe in Story Mode or test your reflexes in Infinite Run. Take on three challenging minigames: <i>All Sides</i> tests your reaction time, <i>Planet Hop</i> requires precision, and <i>Zero-Gravity Pool</i> brings strategic challenges in weightlessness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/11b142342bf4ec5812acfc8c9385aff0.poster.avif?t=1754410258\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/11b142342bf4ec5812acfc8c9385aff0.webm?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560680/extras/11b142342bf4ec5812acfc8c9385aff0.mp4?t=1754410258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> – Embark on an immersive journey through the universe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relic Collection</strong> – Discover and catalog unique space artifacts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill Tree</strong> – Enhance your journey with strategic upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of Skins</strong> – Unlock unique outfits for your character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space Challenges</strong> – Overcome obstacles and prove your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Territory Exploration</strong> – Conquer and discover new regions of space.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progress and Achievements</strong> – Complete objectives and unlock trophies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller Support</strong> – Compatible with Xbox 360, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, and PlayStation 4/5 (Bluetooth and USB).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Space holds many secrets... are you ready to uncover them?</strong></h2>",
